               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t16871207-37-defend170" type="defendantName">
                  John 
                  Markes
               <interp inst="t16871207-37-defend170" type="surname" value="Markes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-defend170" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-defend170" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             of the Parish of <placeName id="t16871207-37-defloc168">St. Martins in the Fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16871207-37-defloc168" type="placeName" value="St. Martins in the Fields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16871207-37-defloc168" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16871207-37-defend170 t16871207-37-defloc168"></join>, was Indicted for <rs id="t16871207-37-off169" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-off169" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-off169" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing on the <rs id="t16871207-37-cd170" type="crimeDate">24th. of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16871207-37-off169 t16871207-37-cd170"></join> last a pair of Velvet Breeches, value 15 s. one Holland Shirt value 15 s. and other things
            </rs>, the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t16871207-37-victim172" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     H ford
                  <interp inst="t16871207-37-victim172" type="surname" value="H ford"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-victim172" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-victim172" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16871207-37-off169 t16871207-37-victim172"></join>
                  </persName>
               
            . He confessed he sold the Breeches to a Broker in the Middle row in Holbourn, and pleaded that he was in Drink when he did the Fact. He was brought in <rs id="t16871207-37-verdict171" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-verdict171" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16871207-37-verdict171" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               guilty to the value of 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
